{"type":null,"faqId":49892,"title":"华为智能手表_手表支持手势唤醒屏幕吗？如何唤醒？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body17741116\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329186__p57264849\">您可以通过翻腕、抬腕等倾斜手腕的动作来唤醒屏幕。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329186__p45621593\">在Android Wear 中国版app中点击进入设置界面 <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c511_i7ee5.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span>，在 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329186__b66497301174651\">设备设置</strong> 中选择已连接HUAWEI WATCH，勾选 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329186__b11799891174710\">倾斜即可唤醒屏幕。</strong></p><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329186__note7941156\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c512_wfe3e.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p class=\"text\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329186__p32693553\">如果您开启了影院模式，则只能通过按压表冠来唤醒屏幕。</p></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":636,"faqType":"屏幕显示类","useful":3,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329186","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448616654000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":95,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"唤醒，屏幕，手势","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}